      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/japan-s-10-year-bond-yield-reaches-highest-since-june-2009</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国的债券扩大了溃败，随着柏林历史性计划释放数千亿欧元的国防和基础设施的历史性计划，全球债务市场滑行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/japan-s-10-year-bond-yield-reaches-highest-since-june-2009</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 00:27:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
